
namespace Android.Support.V4.View
{
    /// <summary>
    /// A class that contains extension methods to wrap events for classes contained within the <see cref = "Android.Support.V4.View"/> namespace.
    /// </summary>
    public static class EventExtensions
    {
        /// <summary>
        /// A wrapper class which wraps all the events contained within the <see cref = "global::Android.Support.V4.View.ViewPager"/> class.
        /// </summary>
        public static ViewPagerEvents Events(this global::Android.Support.V4.View.ViewPager item) => new ViewPagerEvents(item);
    }

    /// <summary>
    /// A class which wraps the events contained within the <see cref = "global::Android.Support.V4.View.ViewPager"/> class as observables.
    /// </summary>
    public class ViewPagerEvents : global::Android.Views.ViewGroupEvents
    {
        private readonly global::Android.Support.V4.View.ViewPager _data;
        /// <summary>
        /// Initializes a new instance of the <see cref = "global::Android.Support.V4.View.ViewPager"/> class.
        /// </summary>
        /// <param name = "data">The class that is being wrapped.</param>
        public ViewPagerEvents(global::Android.Support.V4.View.ViewPager data)
        {
            _data = data;
        }

        /// <summary>
        /// Gets an observable which signals when the <see cref = "Android.Support.V4.View.ViewPager.AdapterChange"/> event triggers.
        /// </summary>
        public global::System.IObservable<global::Android.Support.V4.View.ViewPager.AdapterChangeEventArgs> AdapterChange => global::System.Reactive.Linq.Observable.FromEvent<global::System.EventHandler<global::Android.Support.V4.View.ViewPager.AdapterChangeEventArgs>, global::Android.Support.V4.View.ViewPager.AdapterChangeEventArgs>(eventHandler =>
        {
            void Handler(object sender, global::Android.Support.V4.View.ViewPager.AdapterChangeEventArgs e) => eventHandler(e);
            return Handler;
        }

        , x => _data.AdapterChange += x, x => _data.AdapterChange -= x);
        /// <summary>
        /// Gets an observable which signals when the <see cref = "Android.Support.V4.View.ViewPager.PageScrolled"/> event triggers.
        /// </summary>
        public global::System.IObservable<global::Android.Support.V4.View.ViewPager.PageScrolledEventArgs> PageScrolled => global::System.Reactive.Linq.Observable.FromEvent<global::System.EventHandler<global::Android.Support.V4.View.ViewPager.PageScrolledEventArgs>, global::Android.Support.V4.View.ViewPager.PageScrolledEventArgs>(eventHandler =>
        {
            void Handler(object sender, global::Android.Support.V4.View.ViewPager.PageScrolledEventArgs e) => eventHandler(e);
            return Handler;
        }

        , x => _data.PageScrolled += x, x => _data.PageScrolled -= x);
        /// <summary>
        /// Gets an observable which signals when the <see cref = "Android.Support.V4.View.ViewPager.PageScrollStateChanged"/> event triggers.
        /// </summary>
        public global::System.IObservable<global::Android.Support.V4.View.ViewPager.PageScrollStateChangedEventArgs> PageScrollStateChanged => global::System.Reactive.Linq.Observable.FromEvent<global::System.EventHandler<global::Android.Support.V4.View.ViewPager.PageScrollStateChangedEventArgs>, global::Android.Support.V4.View.ViewPager.PageScrollStateChangedEventArgs>(eventHandler =>
        {
            void Handler(object sender, global::Android.Support.V4.View.ViewPager.PageScrollStateChangedEventArgs e) => eventHandler(e);
            return Handler;
        }

        , x => _data.PageScrollStateChanged += x, x => _data.PageScrollStateChanged -= x);
        /// <summary>
        /// Gets an observable which signals when the <see cref = "Android.Support.V4.View.ViewPager.PageSelected"/> event triggers.
        /// </summary>

namespace Android.Views
{
    /// <summary>
    /// A class that contains extension methods to wrap events for classes contained within the <see cref = "Android.Views"/> namespace.
    /// </summary>
    public static class EventExtensions
    {
        /// <summary>
        /// A wrapper class which wraps all the events contained within the <see cref = "global::Android.Views.View"/> class.
        /// </summary>
        public static ViewEvents Events(this global::Android.Views.View item) => new ViewEvents(item);
        /// <summary>
        /// A wrapper class which wraps all the events contained within the <see cref = "global::Android.Views.ViewGroup"/> class.
        /// </summary>
        public static ViewGroupEvents Events(this global::Android.Views.ViewGroup item) => new ViewGroupEvents(item);
    }

    /// <summary>

        {
            _data = data;
        }

    /// <summary>
    /// A class which wraps the events contained within the <see cref = "global::Android.Views.ViewGroup"/> class as observables.
    /// </summary>
    public class ViewGroupEvents : global::Android.Views.ViewEvents
    {
        private readonly global::Android.Views.ViewGroup _data;
        /// <summary>
        /// Initializes a new instance of the <see cref = "global::Android.Views.ViewGroup"/> class.
        /// </summary>
        /// <param name = "data">The class that is being wrapped.</param>
        public ViewGroupEvents(global::Android.Views.ViewGroup data)
        {

    {

namespace Uno.UI
{
    /// <summary>
    /// A class that contains extension methods to wrap events for classes contained within the <see cref = "Uno.UI"/> namespace.
    /// </summary>
    public static class EventExtensions
    {
        /// <summary>
        /// A wrapper class which wraps all the events contained within the <see cref = "global::Uno.UI.BaseActivity"/> class.
        /// </summary>
        public static BaseActivityEvents Events(this global::Uno.UI.BaseActivity item) => new BaseActivityEvents(item);
        /// <summary>
        /// A wrapper class which wraps all the events contained within the <see cref = "global::Uno.UI.BaseFragment"/> class.
        /// </summary>
        public static BaseFragmentEvents Events(this global::Uno.UI.BaseFragment item) => new BaseFragmentEvents(item);
    }

    /// <summary>
    /// A class which wraps the events contained within the <see cref = "global::Uno.UI.BaseActivity"/> class as observables.
    /// </summary>
    public class BaseActivityEvents
    {
        private readonly global::Uno.UI.BaseActivity _data;
        /// <summary>
        /// Initializes a new instance of the <see cref = "global::Uno.UI.BaseActivity"/> class.
        /// </summary>
        /// <param name = "data">The class that is being wrapped.</param>
        public BaseActivityEvents(global::Uno.UI.BaseActivity data)
        {
            _data = data;
        }

        /// <summary>
        /// Gets an observable which signals when the <see cref = "Uno.UI.BaseActivity.ActionModeFinished"/> event triggers.
        /// </summary>

        {

            return Handler;
        }

        , x => _data.ActionModeFinished += x, x => _data.ActionModeFinished -= x);
        /// <summary>
        /// Gets an observable which signals when the <see cref = "Uno.UI.BaseActivity.ActionModeStarted"/> event triggers.
        /// </summary>

            void Handler(object sender, global::Android.Views.ActionMode e) => eventHandler(e);
            return Handler;
        }

        , x => _data.ActionModeStarted += x, x => _data.ActionModeStarted -= x);
        /// <summary>
        /// Gets an observable which signals when the <see cref = "Uno.UI.BaseActivity.ActivityReenter"/> event triggers.
        /// </summary>
        public global::System.IObservable<global::Uno.UI.BaseActivity.ActivityReenterEventArgs> ActivityReenter => global::System.Reactive.Linq.Observable.FromEvent<global::System.EventHandler<global::Uno.UI.BaseActivity.ActivityReenterEventArgs>, global::Uno.UI.BaseActivity.ActivityReenterEventArgs>(eventHandler =>
        {
            void Handler(object sender, global::Uno.UI.BaseActivity.ActivityReenterEventArgs e) => eventHandler(e);
            return Handler;
        }

        , x => _data.ActivityReenter += x, x => _data.ActivityReenter -= x);
        /// <summary>
        /// Gets an observable which signals when the <see cref = "Uno.UI.BaseActivity.ActivityResult"/> event triggers.
        /// </summary>

namespace Uno.UI.Controls.Legacy
{
    /// <summary>
    /// A class that contains extension methods to wrap events for classes contained within the <see cref = "Uno.UI.Controls.Legacy"/> namespace.
    /// </summary>
    public static class EventExtensions
    {
        /// <summary>
        /// A wrapper class which wraps all the events contained within the <see cref = "global::Uno.UI.Controls.Legacy.GridView"/> class.
        /// </summary>
        public static GridViewEvents Events(this global::Uno.UI.Controls.Legacy.GridView item) => new GridViewEvents(item);
        /// <summary>
        /// A wrapper class which wraps all the events contained within the <see cref = "global::Uno.UI.Controls.Legacy.HorizontalGridView"/> class.
        /// </summary>
        public static HorizontalGridViewEvents Events(this global::Uno.UI.Controls.Legacy.HorizontalGridView item) => new HorizontalGridViewEvents(item);
        /// <summary>
        /// A wrapper class which wraps all the events contained within the <see cref = "global::Uno.UI.Controls.Legacy.HorizontalListView"/> class.
        /// </summary>
        public static HorizontalListViewEvents Events(this global::Uno.UI.Controls.Legacy.HorizontalListView item) => new HorizontalListViewEvents(item);
        /// <summary>
        /// A wrapper class which wraps all the events contained within the <see cref = "global::Uno.UI.Controls.Legacy.ListView"/> class.
        /// </summary>
        public static ListViewEvents Events(this global::Uno.UI.Controls.Legacy.ListView item) => new ListViewEvents(item);
    }

namespace Uno.Xaml
{
    /// <summary>
    /// A class that contains extension methods to wrap events for classes contained within the <see cref = "Uno.Xaml"/> namespace.
    /// </summary>
    public static class EventExtensions
    {
        /// <summary>
        /// A wrapper class which wraps all the events contained within the <see cref = "global::Uno.Xaml.IXamlNameResolver"/> class.
        /// </summary>
        public static IXamlNameResolverEvents Events(this global::Uno.Xaml.IXamlNameResolver item) => new IXamlNameResolverEvents(item);
    }

    /// <summary>
    /// A class which wraps the events contained within the <see cref = "global::Uno.Xaml.IXamlNameResolver"/> class as observables.
    /// </summary>
    public class IXamlNameResolverEvents
    {
        private readonly global::Uno.Xaml.IXamlNameResolver _data;
        /// <summary>
        /// Initializes a new instance of the <see cref = "global::Uno.Xaml.IXamlNameResolver"/> class.
        /// </summary>
        /// <param name = "data">The class that is being wrapped.</param>
        public IXamlNameResolverEvents(global::Uno.Xaml.IXamlNameResolver data)
        {
            _data = data;
        }

        /// <summary>
        /// Gets an observable which signals when the <see cref = "Uno.Xaml.IXamlNameResolver.OnNameScopeInitializationComplete"/> event triggers.
        /// </summary>
        public global::System.IObservable<global::System.EventArgs> OnNameScopeInitializationComplete => global::System.Reactive.Linq.Observable.FromEvent<global::System.EventHandler, global::System.EventArgs>(eventHandler =>
        {
            void Handler(object sender, global::System.EventArgs e) => eventHandler(e);
            return Handler;
        }

        , x => _data.OnNameScopeInitializationComplete += x, x => _data.OnNameScopeInitializationComplete -= x);
    }
}

namespace Windows.ApplicationModel
{
    /// <summary>
    /// A class that contains extension methods to wrap events for classes contained within the <see cref = "Windows.ApplicationModel"/> namespace.
    /// </summary>
    public static class EventExtensions
    {
        /// <summary>
        /// A wrapper class which wraps all the events contained within the <see cref = "global::Windows.ApplicationModel.PackageCatalog"/> class.
        /// </summary>
        public static PackageCatalogEvents Events(this global::Windows.ApplicationModel.PackageCatalog item) => new PackageCatalogEvents(item);
    }

    /// <summary>
    /// A class that contains extension methods to wrap events for classes contained within the <see cref = "Windows.Devices.PointOfService.Provider"/> namespace.
    /// </summary>

    {
        /// <summary>
        /// A wrapper class which wraps all the events contained within the <see cref = "global::Windows.Devices.PointOfService.Provider.BarcodeScannerFrameReader"/> class.
        /// </summary>
        public static BarcodeScannerFrameReaderEvents Events(this global::Windows.Devices.PointOfService.Provider.BarcodeScannerFrameReader item) => new BarcodeScannerFrameReaderEvents(item);
        /// <summary>
        /// A wrapper class which wraps all the events contained within the <see cref = "global::Windows.Devices.PointOfService.Provider.BarcodeScannerProviderConnection"/> class.
        /// </summary>
        public static BarcodeScannerProviderConnectionEvents Events(this global::Windows.Devices.PointOfService.Provider.BarcodeScannerProviderConnection item) => new BarcodeScannerProviderConnectionEvents(item);
    }

namespace Windows.Gaming.Input
{
    /// <summary>
    /// A class that contains extension methods to wrap events for classes contained within the <see cref = "Windows.Gaming.Input"/> namespace.
    /// </summary>
    public static class EventExtensions
    {
        /// <summary>
        /// A wrapper class which wraps all the events contained within the <see cref = "global::Windows.Gaming.Input.ArcadeStick"/> class.
        /// </summary>
        public static ArcadeStickEvents Events(this global::Windows.Gaming.Input.ArcadeStick item) => new ArcadeStickEvents(item);
        /// <summary>
        /// A wrapper class which wraps all the events contained within the <see cref = "global::Windows.Gaming.Input.FlightStick"/> class.
        /// </summary>
        public static FlightStickEvents Events(this global::Windows.Gaming.Input.FlightStick item) => new FlightStickEvents(item);
        /// <summary>
        /// A wrapper class which wraps all the events contained within the <see cref = "global::Windows.Gaming.Input.Gamepad"/> class.
        /// </summary>
        public static GamepadEvents Events(this global::Windows.Gaming.Input.Gamepad item) => new GamepadEvents(item);
        /// <summary>
        /// A wrapper class which wraps all the events contained within the <see cref = "global::Windows.Gaming.Input.IGameController"/> class.
        /// </summary>
        public static IGameControllerEvents Events(this global::Windows.Gaming.Input.IGameController item) => new IGameControllerEvents(item);
        /// <summary>
        /// A wrapper class which wraps all the events contained within the <see cref = "global::Windows.Gaming.Input.RacingWheel"/> class.
        /// </summary>
        public static RacingWheelEvents Events(this global::Windows.Gaming.Input.RacingWheel item) => new RacingWheelEvents(item);
        /// <summary>
        /// A wrapper class which wraps all the events contained within the <see cref = "global::Windows.Gaming.Input.RawGameController"/> class.
        /// </summary>
        public static RawGameControllerEvents Events(this global::Windows.Gaming.Input.RawGameController item) => new RawGameControllerEvents(item);
        /// <summary>
        /// A wrapper class which wraps all the events contained within the <see cref = "global::Windows.Gaming.Input.UINavigationController"/> class.
        /// </summary>
        public static UINavigationControllerEvents Events(this global::Windows.Gaming.Input.UINavigationController item) => new UINavigationControllerEvents(item);
    }

namespace Windows.Media.PlayTo
{
    /// <summary>
    /// A class that contains extension methods to wrap events for classes contained within the <see cref = "Windows.Media.PlayTo"/> namespace.
    /// </summary>
    public static class EventExtensions
    {
        /// <summary>
        /// A wrapper class which wraps all the events contained within the <see cref = "global::Windows.Media.PlayTo.PlayToConnection"/> class.
        /// </summary>
        public static PlayToConnectionEvents Events(this global::Windows.Media.PlayTo.PlayToConnection item) => new PlayToConnectionEvents(item);
        /// <summary>
        /// A wrapper class which wraps all the events contained within the <see cref = "global::Windows.Media.PlayTo.PlayToManager"/> class.
        /// </summary>
        public static PlayToManagerEvents Events(this global::Windows.Media.PlayTo.PlayToManager item) => new PlayToManagerEvents(item);
        /// <summary>
        /// A wrapper class which wraps all the events contained within the <see cref = "global::Windows.Media.PlayTo.PlayToReceiver"/> class.
        /// </summary>
        public static PlayToReceiverEvents Events(this global::Windows.Media.PlayTo.PlayToReceiver item) => new PlayToReceiverEvents(item);
    }

namespace Windows.UI.Input.Inking
{
    /// <summary>
    /// A class that contains extension methods to wrap events for classes contained within the <see cref = "Windows.UI.Input.Inking"/> namespace.
    /// </summary>
    public static class EventExtensions
    {
        /// <summary>
        /// A wrapper class which wraps all the events contained within the <see cref = "global::Windows.UI.Input.Inking.InkPresenter"/> class.
        /// </summary>
        public static InkPresenterEvents Events(this global::Windows.UI.Input.Inking.InkPresenter item) => new InkPresenterEvents(item);
        /// <summary>
        /// A wrapper class which wraps all the events contained within the <see cref = "global::Windows.UI.Input.Inking.InkStrokeInput"/> class.
        /// </summary>
        public static InkStrokeInputEvents Events(this global::Windows.UI.Input.Inking.InkStrokeInput item) => new InkStrokeInputEvents(item);
        /// <summary>
        /// A wrapper class which wraps all the events contained within the <see cref = "global::Windows.UI.Input.Inking.InkUnprocessedInput"/> class.
        /// </summary>
        public static InkUnprocessedInputEvents Events(this global::Windows.UI.Input.Inking.InkUnprocessedInput item) => new InkUnprocessedInputEvents(item);
    }

    /// <summary>
    /// A class which wraps the events contained within the <see cref = "global::Windows.UI.Xaml.Controls.AppBar"/> class as observables.
    /// </summary>
    public class AppBarEvents : global::Windows.UI.Xaml.Controls.ControlEvents
    {
        private readonly global::Windows.UI.Xaml.Controls.AppBar _data;
        /// <summary>
        /// Initializes a new instance of the <see cref = "global::Windows.UI.Xaml.Controls.AppBar"/> class.
        /// </summary>
        /// <param name = "data">The class that is being wrapped.</param>
        public AppBarEvents(global::Windows.UI.Xaml.Controls.AppBar data)
        {
            _data = data;
        }

        /// <summary>
        /// Gets an observable which signals when the <see cref = "Windows.UI.Xaml.Controls.AppBar.Closed"/> event triggers.
        /// </summary>
        public global::System.IObservable<object> Closed => global::System.Reactive.Linq.Observable.FromEvent<global::System.EventHandler<object>, object>(eventHandler =>
        {
            void Handler(object sender, object e) => eventHandler(e);
            return Handler;
        }

        , x => _data.Closed += x, x => _data.Closed -= x);
        /// <summary>
        /// Gets an observable which signals when the <see cref = "Windows.UI.Xaml.Controls.AppBar.Closing"/> event triggers.
        /// </summary>
        public global::System.IObservable<object> Closing => global::System.Reactive.Linq.Observable.FromEvent<global::System.EventHandler<object>, object>(eventHandler =>
        {
            void Handler(object sender, object e) => eventHandler(e);
            return Handler;
        }

        , x => _data.Closing += x, x => _data.Closing -= x);
        /// <summary>
        /// Gets an observable which signals when the <see cref = "Windows.UI.Xaml.Controls.AppBar.Opened"/> event triggers.
        /// </summary>
        public global::System.IObservable<object> Opened => global::System.Reactive.Linq.Observable.FromEvent<global::System.EventHandler<object>, object>(eventHandler =>
        {
            void Handler(object sender, object e) => eventHandler(e);
            return Handler;
        }

        , x => _data.Opened += x, x => _data.Opened -= x);
        /// <summary>
        /// Gets an observable which signals when the <see cref = "Windows.UI.Xaml.Controls.AppBar.Opening"/> event triggers.
        /// </summary>
        public global::System.IObservable<object> Opening => global::System.Reactive.Linq.Observable.FromEvent<global::System.EventHandler<object>, object>(eventHandler =>
        {
            void Handler(object sender, object e) => eventHandler(e);
            return Handler;
        }

        , x => _data.Opening += x, x => _data.Opening -= x);
    }

    /// <summary>
    /// A class which wraps the events contained within the <see cref = "global::Windows.UI.Xaml.Controls.AutoSuggestBox"/> class as observables.
    /// </summary>
    public class AutoSuggestBoxEvents : global::Windows.UI.Xaml.Controls.ControlEvents
    {
        private readonly global::Windows.UI.Xaml.Controls.AutoSuggestBox _data;
        /// <summary>
        /// Initializes a new instance of the <see cref = "global::Windows.UI.Xaml.Controls.AutoSuggestBox"/> class.
        /// </summary>
        /// <param name = "data">The class that is being wrapped.</param>
        public AutoSuggestBoxEvents(global::Windows.UI.Xaml.Controls.AutoSuggestBox data)

{
    /// <summary>
    /// A class that contains extension methods to wrap events for classes contained within the <see cref = "Windows.UI.Xaml.Media.Animation"/> namespace.
    /// </summary>
    public static class EventExtensions
    {
        /// <summary>
        /// A wrapper class which wraps all the events contained within the <see cref = "global::Windows.UI.Xaml.Media.Animation.ColorKeyFrame"/> class.
        /// </summary>
        public static ColorKeyFrameEvents Events(this global::Windows.UI.Xaml.Media.Animation.ColorKeyFrame item) => new ColorKeyFrameEvents(item);
        /// <summary>
        /// A wrapper class which wraps all the events contained within the <see cref = "global::Windows.UI.Xaml.Media.Animation.ConnectedAnimation"/> class.
        /// </summary>
        public static ConnectedAnimationEvents Events(this global::Windows.UI.Xaml.Media.Animation.ConnectedAnimation item) => new ConnectedAnimationEvents(item);
        /// <summary>
        /// A wrapper class which wraps all the events contained within the <see cref = "global::Windows.UI.Xaml.Media.Animation.DoubleKeyFrame"/> class.
        /// </summary>
        public static DoubleKeyFrameEvents Events(this global::Windows.UI.Xaml.Media.Animation.DoubleKeyFrame item) => new DoubleKeyFrameEvents(item);
        /// <summary>
        /// A wrapper class which wraps all the events contained within the <see cref = "global::Windows.UI.Xaml.Media.Animation.EasingFunctionBase"/> class.
        /// </summary>
        public static EasingFunctionBaseEvents Events(this global::Windows.UI.Xaml.Media.Animation.EasingFunctionBase item) => new EasingFunctionBaseEvents(item);
        /// <summary>
        /// A wrapper class which wraps all the events contained within the <see cref = "global::Windows.UI.Xaml.Media.Animation.KeySpline"/> class.
        /// </summary>
        public static KeySplineEvents Events(this global::Windows.UI.Xaml.Media.Animation.KeySpline item) => new KeySplineEvents(item);
        /// <summary>
        /// A wrapper class which wraps all the events contained within the <see cref = "global::Windows.UI.Xaml.Media.Animation.NavigationTransitionInfo"/> class.
        /// </summary>

        /// <summary>
        /// A wrapper class which wraps all the events contained within the <see cref = "global::Windows.UI.Xaml.Media.Animation.ObjectKeyFrame"/> class.

        /// A wrapper class which wraps all the events contained within the <see cref = "global::Windows.Web.UI.IWebViewControl"/> class.
        /// </summary>
        public static IWebViewControlEvents Events(this global::Windows.Web.UI.IWebViewControl item) => new IWebViewControlEvents(item);
    }

namespace Windows.Web.UI.Interop
{
    /// <summary>
    /// A class that contains extension methods to wrap events for classes contained within the <see cref = "Windows.Web.UI.Interop"/> namespace.
    /// </summary>
    public static class EventExtensions
    {
        /// <summary>
        /// A wrapper class which wraps all the events contained within the <see cref = "global::Windows.Web.UI.Interop.WebViewControl"/> class.
        /// </summary>
        public static WebViewControlEvents Events(this global::Windows.Web.UI.Interop.WebViewControl item) => new WebViewControlEvents(item);
        /// <summary>
        /// A wrapper class which wraps all the events contained within the <see cref = "global::Windows.Web.UI.Interop.WebViewControlProcess"/> class.
        /// </summary>
        public static WebViewControlProcessEvents Events(this global::Windows.Web.UI.Interop.WebViewControlProcess item) => new WebViewControlProcessEvents(item);
    }
